    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she\u2019s a total stunner! This car is in truly flawless condition; it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and meticulously detailed. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
