    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, appearing as though it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of pristine materials; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or creasing, and still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from authorized specialists. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail has been meticulously maintained. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment ready for its next discerning owner.",
      "price": 46500.0,
