      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, preserved in true collector condition. At its heart is the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure variable double-VANOS, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a documented service history including critical preventative maintenance: rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and structural subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise, mechanical shift throws, paired with a perfectly calibrated M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, retaining factory-spec bushings and dampers for unparalleled steering feedback. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation and an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a turnkey specimen for the discerning purist.",
